===Returning starters===
USC returns 18 starters in 2012, including nine on offense, seven on defense, and both the starting kicker and punter.<ref name="espnladepth"/>  Key departures included [[offensive tackle]] [[Matt Kalil]], [[Fullback (American football)|fullback]] [[Rhett Ellison]], [[running back]] Marc Tyler, [[defensive end]] [[Nick Perry (American football)|Nick Perry]], [[linebacker]] Chris Galippo, [[defensive tackle]] DaJohn Harris, and [[nose tackle]] Christian Tupou.  Before the season, starting cornerback [[Isiah Wiley]] was declared academically ineligible, and starting left DE Devon Kennard suffered a pectoral injury that could force him to redshirt this season.<ref name="specialists"/>
