{{See also|2012 Notre Dame Fighting Irish football team}}
In 2011, USC defeated the Notre Dame Fighting Irish, 31<U+2013>17.  USC has won nine of the last ten meetings against Notre Dame. ESPN's "[[College GameDay]]" show was at the game.
